### Application Entry Point

#### [NEW] [entrypoint.swift](file:///home/hronop/node/moment/vapor-api/Sources/App/entrypoint.swift)
- Конфигурация Fluent PostgreSQL (из `DATABASE_URL` env)
- Регистрация middleware (CORS, trusted proxy headers)
- Привязка к `0.0.0.0:8080`

#### [NEW] [configure.swift](file:///home/hronop/node/moment/vapor-api/Sources/App/configure.swift)
- `app.databases.use(.postgres(url: env.DATABASE_URL))`
- `app.middleware.use(CORSMiddleware(...))`
- Регистрация контроллеров на `/api/**`

#### [NEW] [routes.swift](file:///home/hronop/node/moment/vapor-api/Sources/App/routes.swift)
Регистрация маршрутов:
```swift
let api = app.grouped("api")
let protected = api.grouped(JWTAuthMiddleware())
let admin = protected.grouped(AdminMiddleware())

protected.grouped("files").get("**", use: FileController.download)
admin.grouped("seaweed-proxy").get("**", use: SeaweedProxyController.proxy)
api.get("health", use: HealthController.check)
```

